text.tspan: WASHA, derived from the word “SWAyam SHAkti”, embodies the essence of self-empowerment.
We provide a platform to market the products made by marginalized communities including
women, Persons with Disabilities (PwDs) and LGBTQ+ individuals.

tspan.tspan: ith every purchase, you become a part of our mission to empower marginalized
communities, giving them a platform to showcase their incredible skills and talents.
